        "content": "Web search results for query: \"terminal AI coding agent repo-aware February 2026 launch\"\n\nI'll search for information about this terminal AI coding agent with repo-aware capabilities and the February 2026 launch timeline.\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"QwenLM/Qwen3.5 - GitHub\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen3.5\"},{\"title\":\"opencode\",\"url\":\"https://gitee.com/devai/opencode\"},{\"title\":\"agentic terminal coding\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnblogs.com/itech/p/19274858\"},{\"title\":\"OpenCode与其他终端AI工具对比：为什么开发者应该选择这款终极终端助手[特殊字符]\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/gitblog_00440/article/details/153712547\"},{\"title\":\"The Future of Software Development in the AI Era\",\"url\":\"https://dev.to/alessandro_benigni/the-future-of-software-development-in-the-ai-era-nn2\"},{\"title\":\"opencode01\",\"url\":\"https://gitee.com/xu13337727768/opencode01\"},{\"title\":\"BNLNPPS/awesome-terminals-ai\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/BNLNPPS/awesome-terminals-ai\"},{\"title\":\"2026年01月27日最热门的开源项目(Github)\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/yao1500/article/details/157458476\"},{\"title\":\"命令行AI助手大比拼\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7579095566900248616\"},{\"title\":\"2026年02月02日最热门的开源项目(Github)\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/yao1500/article/details/157681619\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, I found several terminal-based AI coding agents, though none specifically mention a February 2026 launch. Here are the key findings:\n\n## **OpenCode** \n**Most relevant match** - An AI coding agent built specifically for the terminal:\n- **Launch/Activity**: Active in early 2026 (package updates on January 23 and 31, 2026)\n- **Repository**: https://github.com/sst/opencode\n- **Key Features**:\n  - Native Terminal UI (TUI)\n  - LSP-enabled for code awareness\n  - Multi-session support\n  - Works with 75+ LLM providers\n  - Repository-aware functionality\n  - Share links for debugging\n  - Integration with Claude Pro/Max\n\n## **Qwen Code**\n- **Launch**: February 2026 (Qwen3.5 release dated February 2026)\n- **Repository**: https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen3.5\n- **Description**: Open-source AI agent for the terminal, optimized for Qwen models\n\n## **Anthropic Claude Code**\n- **Launch**: Late February 2025 (not 2026)\n- **Repository**: https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code\n- **Features**: Repo-aware, understands your codebase, executes routine tasks through natural language\n\n## Other Notable Terminal AI Agents:\n- **Aider** - AI pair programming in terminal\n- **Cursor CLI** - AI-assisted coding workflows\n- **Cline CLI** - Autonomous coding agent for CLI\n- **Continue.Dev CLI** - Context-aware coding assistant\n- **Plandex** - Plans and executes complex tasks across codebases\n- **Goose CLI** - Open-source agent from Block\n\n**Note**: While there are several terminal AI coding agents with repo-aware capabilities launched or updated in early 2026, none specifically advertise a \"February 2026 launch\" date. OpenCode shows the most recent activity in January 2026 with repo-aware features.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
