Both products are from JetBrains and represent significant updates to their AI tooling ecosystem. Other AI coding-related releases from February 2026 (such as GitHub Agentic Workflows, OpenAI Frontier, and Claude Opus 4.6) were launched earlier in the month (February 5-6) and thus fall outside the 14-day window.

